# ðŸ”¹ Architecture Overview

```text
    S3 Bucket Change Event
               |
               v
       CloudTrail Logs
               |
               v
        EventBridge Rule
               |
               v
     Lambda Auto-Remediator
               |
               v
    - Check bucket ACL/public access
    - Enforce Block Public Access
    - Log + (optional) notify
